BT /F1 10 Tf 82 614 Td (IRC Sections 162\(m\) and 409A.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 588 Td (The examination focuses on deferred compensation agreements, performance-based incentive) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 574 Td (structures, and supplemental executive retirement plans \(SERPs\) for the top five named) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 560 Td (executive officers.) Tj ET
