BT /F1 10 Tf 82 516 Td (a\) All employment agreements, amendments, and side letters for Named Executive Officers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 502 Td (\(NEOs\) effective during tax year 2023.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 488 Td (b\) Schedule of all deferred compensation balances as of December 31, 2023, including) Tj ET
