BT /F2 14 Tf 72 382 Td (3. Relevant IRC Provisions) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 360 Td (IRC Section 162\(m\) limits the deduction for compensation paid to covered employees to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 346 Td ($1,000,000. Following the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act of 2017, the performance-based) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 332 Td (compensation exception was eliminated for tax years beginning after December 31, 2017,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 318 Td (subject to transition relief for binding contracts in effect on November 2, 2017.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 292 Td (IRC Section 409A imposes requirements on the timing of deferral elections and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 278 Td (distributions from nonqualified deferred compensation plans. Failure to comply may result) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 264 Td (in immediate income inclusion plus a 20% additional tax.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 72 242 Td (4. Response Deadline) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 220 Td (Please provide the requested documents within 30 calendar days of receipt of this IDR. If) Tj ET
